</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Boolean</strong><br />
Puﾃｲ assumere solo due valori: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">true</code> o <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">false</code>.
